# Cloudflare Pages SPA Routing
# All routes fall back to index.html so React Router handles them client-side
# Without this, direct URL visits (e.g. /tool/chatgpt) return 404 on Cloudflare Pages

# Redirect trailing slash to canonical (no trailing slash)
/browse/   /browse   301
/compare/  /compare  301
/submit/   /submit   301
/blog/     /blog     301
/about/    /about    301
/contact/  /contact  301
/privacy/  /privacy  301
/terms/    /terms    301

# SPA fallback — must be last
/*    /index.html   200
